- for cards use [CustomCard.tsx](mdc:src/app/_components/atoms/cards/CustomCard.tsx) 
- with CustomCard use defaultPadding enabled by default unless you want it to be specific
- use [button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/button.tsx) for buttons and size prop for different sizes
- use [Typography.tsx](mdc:src/components/Typography.tsx) component for texts 
- use [DataStatus.tsx](mdc:src/app/_components/molecules/alerts/DataStatus.tsx) for sticker and ducks 
